thread.title: BRIEF-Q-Free receives NOK 21 mln order from Australia
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Q-Free receives NOK 21 mln order from Australia | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Q-Free receives NOK 21 mln order from Australia
text:
Sept 16 Q-Free ASA :
* Receives service and maintenance order in Australia worth 21 million Norwegian crowns ($2.56 million)
* Order is extension of current agreement, for a period of three years, with an option for further extension of two years
